    "title": "Eliya",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "eliya",
    "language": "swh",
    "content": "<p>Eliya kutoka Mtishbi alikuwa nabii katika Israeli wakati wa utawala wa Ahabu na Ahazia, kuanzia 874 hadi 852 Kabla ya Kristo (KK). Jina lake linamaanisha &quot;Mungu wangu ni Yahweh.&quot; Alionyesha kwamba Bwana ndiye Mubgu wa kweli na akahimiza Israeli kumrudia Bwana.</p><p>Chini ya utawala wa Ahabu na Yezebeli, Waisraeli walianza kumwabudu Baali, mungu wa Wakanaani anayehusishwa na uzazi, dhoruba, na mvua. Kwa sababu hiyo, Mungu alileta ukame katika Israeli (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs17:1\">1 Wafalme 17:1</a>). Eliya alijificha hadi ukame ulipomalizika, na Mungu alimlinda. Katika kipindi hiki, alikaa na mjane huko Sarepta, mji ulioko katika eneo la nyumbani kwa Yezebeli la Sidoni. Mwana wa mjane alikufa, lakini Eliya alimuombea, na akafufuka (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs17:8-1Kgs17:24\">1 Wafalme 17:8–24</a>).</p><p>Katika mwaka wa tatu wa ukame, Eliya aliwatia changamoto manabii wa Baali kwenye shindano kwenye Mlima Karmeli ili kuonyesha nani alikuwa Mungu wa kweli (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs18:1-1Kgs18:40\">1 Wafalme 18:1–40</a>). Manabii wa Baali walimwita Baali bila mafanikio, wakihangaika kumfanya aonekane, huku Eliya akimdhihaki Baali. Ilipofika zamu ya Eliya, alimimina maji juu ya dhabihu yake na akaomba sala rahisi, yenye nguvu. Moto mara moja uliteketeza sadaka hiyo. Watu wa Israeli walimwabudu Bwana na, kufuatia maelekezo ya Eliya, waliwaua manabii wa Baali. Kisha Eliya akaomba mvua, na ukame ukaisha (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs18:41-1Kgs18:46\">1 Wafalme 18:41–46</a>).</p><p>Licha ya nguvu kuu za Mungu, Ahabu na Yezebeli waliendelea kupotosha Israeli. Yezebeli alikasirika kwa sababu manabii wake waliuawa (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs19:1-1Kgs19:2\">1 Wafalme 19:1–2</a>). Alimtishia Eliya, ambaye alikimbilia jangwani na kumwomba Mungu amalize maisha yake. Badala yake, malaika walimlisha hadi alipofika Mlima Sinai. Eliya alilalamika kwamba alikuwa nabii pekee aliyebaki na kwamba maisha yake yalikuwa hatarini. Mungu alimtia moyo kwa sauti ya upole, akampa Habari Njema, na kumtuma arudi kutumikia (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs19:3-1Kgs19:18\">1 Wafalme 19:3–18</a>).</p><p>Eliya alikuwa amejitolea sana kwa Mungu wa kweli. Alimfundisha msaidizi wake aliyeitwa Elisha. Mwisho wa maisha ya Eliya duniani, hakufa bali alichukuliwa mbinguni kwa gari la moto (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs2:11-2Kgs2:12\">2 Wafalme 2:11–12</a>). Elisha alichukua jukumu la Eliya kama nabii na aliendelea kupinga ibada ya uongo katika Israeli (tazama <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs2:1-2Kgs9:13\">2 Wafalme 2:1–9:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs13:14-2Kgs13:25\">13:14–25</a>).</p><p>Agano la Kale linahitimishwa na tumaini kwamba Eliya atarudi kabla ya Siku ya Bwana (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mal4:5-Mal4:6\">Malaki 4:5–6</a>). Yohana Mbatizaji alitimiza sehemu ya matarajio haya (tazama <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt11:7-Matt11:14\">Mathayo 11:7–14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt17:10-Matt17:13\">17:10–13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke1:17\">Luka 1:17</a>). Eliya alionekana pamoja na Mose wakati wa kubadilika kwa Yesu (wakati sura ya Yesu ilibadilika kuonyesha utukufu wake wa kimungu; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt17:1-Matt17:9\">Mathayo 17:1–9</a>). Katika <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev11:3-Rev11:12\">Ufunuo 11:3–12</a>, mmoja wa mashahidi wawili anaonekana kuwa ama Eliya mwenyewe au mtu kama yeye. Maisha ya Eliya yanaonyesha wema wa Mungu na nguvu ya maombi (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke4:25-Luke4:26\">Luka 4:25–26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom11:2-Rom11:6\">Warumi 11:2–6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas5:17-Jas5:18\">Yakobo 5:17–18</a>).</p><p><u>Sehemu za Kujifunza Zaidi</u></p><p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs17:1-1Kgs19:21\">1 Wafalme 17:1–19:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs21:1-1Kgs21:29\">21:1–29</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs1:1-2Kgs2:25\">2 Wafalme 1:1–2:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs9:36\">9:36</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs10:10\">10:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs10:17\">17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr21:12-2Chr21:15\">2 Mambo ya Nyakati 21:12–15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mal4:5-Mal4:6\">Malaki 4:5–6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt11:14\">Mathayo 11:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt16:14\">16:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt17:1-Matt17:13\">17:1–13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt27:45-Matt27:49\">27:45–49</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark6:15\">Marko 6:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark8:28\">8:28</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark9:2-Mark9:13\">9:2–13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark15:33-Mark15:36\">15:33–36</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke1:17\">Luka 1:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke4:26\">4:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke9:28-Luke9:36\">9:28–36</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John1:19-John1:28\">Yohana 1:19–28</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom11:1-Rom11:6\">Warumi 11:1–6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas5:17\">Yakobo 5:17</a></p>",
